{"tid":1427284,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔係咪太蠢？咁都唔明消防處講咩","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T14:05:33.000Z","uid":56857,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"473c0115929c741a30e1b1335986f489c971aef1","tid":1427284,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"消防處副消防總長（質素保證及管理）鄭瑞安指，示威者投擲汽油彈、燃燒彈等，並在各處縱火。鄭瑞安亦指，示威者縱火的規模漸大，以及焚燒的雜物亦有增加，昨日處理21宗縱火事件。他亦指，有示威者昨日包圍紀律部隊宿舍，並有人在<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紀律部隊宿舍</span></span></strong>縱火，並指宿舍與其他大廈一樣，有長者等老弱婦孺在內。他續指，示威者的行為可造成嚴重後果，並形容相關行為極不負責任。他亦呼籲示威者停止堵塞道路、使用危險品，以及縱火，並呼籲市民遠離相關區域。<br />\n<br />\n多區出現縱火 由其狗屋<br />\n但譴責既 指定<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紀律部隊宿舍</span></span></strong><br />\n到底消防處企係邊面 仲有人唔明嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9f215f21be404bc32da36a29979964c531a5ce","tid":1427284,"uid":51234,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"佢提醒唔好好似白衫人咁無差別傷人"},{"pid":"bcad971ca1ab581707d34429cf55b5fbfad3c2fe","tid":1427284,"uid":123870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b935598aa338ac4e5b4d913954ac5462e40738f","tid":1427284,"uid":277900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"不合作運動之全新演繹<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426175\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b078cc0b8dfeec420fa45306ff88d6cfa6789bfb","tid":1427284,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"岩呀,咩都係曲線,藍絲其實係我地既好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5